    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight">Do small businesses still need email marketing campaigns?</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Yes. Email marketing campaigns help small businesses follow up with leads, bring customers back, promote offers, and stay visible without relying only on social media algorithms.</p>
